s atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNStyle"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNStyle","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy object for the current map style."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" object containing a Boolean value; specifies whether the shape of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" should be wrapped to accomodate coordinates with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"longitudes beyond −180 and 180. The default value is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionwrapscoordinates","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNComputedShapeSource","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"one tile at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that returns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", then add a computed shape source to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the computed shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URL"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNShapeSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSource"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Data source for "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"}}}